column1: # Labelling of the sheets for the two gauges at Mickleton Lime Kiln is ambiguous, so other assignments of sheets to gauges are possible.
# The readings for January and February 1895 are apportioned.
# The readings for July and August 1912 have been adjusted for the day of reading.
# The reading for December 1916 is an estimate and has been omitted.
# The readings for March and April 1919 are estimated and have been omitted.
# A new gauge was installed at the start of 1917.
# See the notes to gauge No 1 regarding the site location.
